Tickets to the Ghostland festival are $55 in advance and $65 on show day and available at the [State Theatre website](https://statetheatreportland.com/events/ghostland/). A two-day ticket, which allows entry to the show at Live at Madrid’s on Sept. 4 and to the Ghostland festival on Sept. 6, is $125.

